cast.overview: Sheffield, England. Gaz, a jobless steelworker in need of quick cash persuades his mates to bare it all in a one-night-only strip show.
cast.title: The Full Monty

details.biography: Theresa recently took a main part in the documentary film about Victoria Climbie. She played the part of Marie Therese Kouao, the 'aunt' of a young African girl, Victoria Climbie, who was abused by the aunt and her partner and died as a result. Film was screened in 2012 as part of a series entitled 'Crimes that shook Britain'.
details.name: Theresa Maduemezia
